-- Cyprus Popular Bank's board submits resignation
-- 
-- Thu Mar 28, 2013 5:47am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/03/28/us-cyprus-popularbank-idUSBRE92R07C20130328

 

 ATHENS  (Reuters) - Cyprus Popular Bank said in an Athens bourse filing on Thursday that its 11-member board resigned. 
 Cyprus's banks will open later on Thursday and operate under capital controls imposed to prevent depositors from emptying the vaults after the island agreed a tough rescue deal with international lenders. (Reporting by Renee Maltezou, editing by George Georgiopoulos)